==Greatest maximum depth by continent==
*'''[[Africa]]''' &mdash; 1: [[Lake Tanganyika|Tanganyika]], 2: [[Lake Malawi|Malawi]], 3: [[Lake Kivu|Kivu]]
*'''[[Antarctica]]''' &mdash; 1: [[Radok Lake]] (surface lake); [[Lake Vostok|Vostok]] (subglacial lake)<ref name=Vostok/>
*'''[[Asia]]''' &mdash; 1: [[Lake Baikal|Baikal]], (2: [[Caspian Sea]]), 3: [[Issyk Kul]], (3: [[Lake Matano|Matano]])
*'''[[Europe]]''' &mdash; 1: [[Hornindalsvatnet]], 2: [[Salsvatnet]], 3: [[Lake Tinn]] 
*'''[[North America]]''' &mdash; 1: [[Great Slave Lake]], 2: [[Crater Lake|Crater]], 3: [[Quesnel Lake|Quesnel]]
:*'''[[Central America]]''' &mdash; 1: [[Lago de Atitlán|Atitlán]], 2: [[Laguna Chicabal|Chicabal]]
*'''[[Oceania]]''' &mdash; 1: [[Lake Hauroko|Hauroko]], 2: [[Lake Manapouri|Manapouri]], 3: [[Lake Te Anau|Te Anau]] 
:*'''[[Australia]]''' &mdash; 1: [[Lake St Clair (Tasmania)|St Clair]]
*'''[[South America]]''' &mdash; 1: [[O'Higgins/San Martín Lake|O'Higgins/San Martín]], 2: [[General Carrera Lake|General Carrera]], 3: [[Lake Argentino|Argentino]]

==Greatest mean depth by continent==
*'''[[Africa]]''' &mdash; 1: [[Lake Tanganyika|Tanganyika]], 2: [[Lake Malawi|Malawi]], 3: [[Lake Kivu|Kivu]]
*'''[[Antarctica]]''' &mdash; 1: [[Lake Vostok|Vostok]]<ref name=Vostok/>
*'''[[Asia]]''' &mdash; 1: [[Lake Baikal|Baikal]], 2: [[Issyk Kul]], 3: [[Karakul (Tajikistan)|Karakul]]
*'''[[Europe]]''' &mdash; 1: [[Hornindalsvatnet]], 2: [[Lake Tinn]], 3: [[Como Lake|Como]]
*'''[[North America]]''' &mdash; 1: [[Crater Lake|Crater]], 2: [[Lake Tahoe|Tahoe]], 3: [[Lake Quesnel|Quesnel]]
*'''[[Oceania]]''' &mdash; 1: [[Kauhakō Crater]]

